			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Origin-Exile3')
			span.sheet-mainbox
			span.sheet-grayable
				span(data-i18n='exile-origin3') Magical accident or side-effect.
		.sheet-move
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Origin-Exile4')
			span.sheet-mainbox
			span.sheet-grayable
				span(data-i18n='exile-origin4') You angered a sorcerer.
		.sheet-move
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Origin-Exile5')
